OL,3,CInvestigation underway into big fire
OL,4,Cin east London
OL,6,FFirefighters are investigating the
OL,7,Fcause of a big fire in Bermondsey on
OL,8,FMonday.
OL,10,FOfficers were responding to the blaze
OL,11,Fat a waste incineration plant, on
OL,12,FLandmann Way.
OL,14,FThe fire was brought under control
OL,15,Fjust before midnight, and caused major
OL,16,Fdisruption to rail services at London
OL,17,FBridge and Charing Cross.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
