OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781093477
OL,3,CInvestigation underway into big fire
OL,4,Cin east London
OL,6,FImages captured near the scene showed
OL,7,Fthick plumes of smoke rising above the
OL,8,Fsurrounding buildings, and the LFB
OL,9,Furged local residents to keep their
OL,10,Fwindows and doors closed.
OL,12,FStation Commander Wayne Bloomfield,
OL,13,Fwho attended the scene, said:
OL,14,F"Firefighters worked hard overnight
OL,15,Fand have now fully extinguished this
OL,16,Ffire.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
