OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781093477
OL,3,CInvestigation underway into big fire
OL,4,Cin east London
OL,6,F"At its height, the fire involved a
OL,7,Flarge amount of refuse and the roof of
OL,8,Fa warehouse unit. A van and a car were
OL,9,Falso destroyed by the fire. One man
OL,10,Fwas treated on scene by London
OL,11,FAmbulance Service.
OL,13,F"Due to the significant amount of
OL,14,Fsmoke in the area, local residents
OL,15,Fwere advised to keep their windows and
OL,16,Fdoors closed.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/4
