OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781093477
OL,3,CInvestigation underway into big fire
OL,4,Cin east London
OL,6,F"Loose embers were also reported,
OL,7,Fwhich is normal during large fires.
OL,8,FResidents were advised to pour water
OL,9,Fonto them if they were concerned about
OL,10,Floose embers on or near their
OL,11,Fproperties, but if they did catch
OL,12,Fsomething alight, to call 999
OL,13,Fimmediately."
